videos.description: Zion Williamson converts the layup after leaping up and grabbing the offensive rebound.
videos.headline: Zion grabs offensive rebound and lays it in

videos.description: Zion Williamson drives and kicks it to RJ Barrett, who knocks down the three from the left wing.
videos.headline: RJ Barrett knocks down 3 for Duke

videos.description: Zion Williamson skies high for the defensive rebound then goes coast to coast for the tough finish in the lane.
videos.headline: Zion goes coast to coast for Duke

videos.description: Duke gets the steal and RJ Barrett throws it up to Zion Williamson, who throws down the monster two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Barrett throws the lob to Zion for huge dunk

videos.description: Duke gets the steal and Marques Bolden finds RJ Barrett for the two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Barrett throws down thunderous dunk

videos.description: Zion Williamson protects the rim with authority by swatting away Josh Caldwell's shot.
videos.headline: Zion gets way up for huge block

videos.description: Duke freshman Cameron Reddish showed off the range by hitting seven 3-pointers in Duke's 94-72 win over Army.
